ail Morris) 在 7 月 4 日即将到来的英国大选中发表讲话</a>，要求选民“互相保护，要有一些他妈的同理心”。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kasabian-glastonbury-2024-secret-set-watch-interview-footage-photos-3770249">卡萨比安确认伍西的秘密设置</a></h2><p>关于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kasabian">Kasabian</a>在 Glastonbury 秘密演出的传闻持续数周后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-kasabian-confirm-rumoured-secret-set-3770077">莱斯特乐队终于在周六下午确认</a>，他们将于下午 6 点在 Woodsies 演出。 </p><figure id="attachment_3770274" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3770274" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3770274" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT.jpg" alt="Kasabian 在 Glastonbury 2024 现场演出。图片来源：NME 的 Andy Ford" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/NMEGlasto24_Kasabian_Woodsies_AFord-69170_EDIT-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3770274" class="wp-caption-text"> Kasabian 在 Glastonbury 2024 现场演出。图片来源：NME 的 Andy Ford</figcaption></figure><p>演出前，现场非常拥挤，以至于歌迷们都被拒之门外，主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/serge-pizzorno">谢尔盖·皮佐诺 (Serge Pizzorno)</a>在演出前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kasabian-glastonbury-2024-secret-set-watch-interview-footage-photos-3770249">接受<em>NME</em>采访</a>时承诺，“这是一个充满力量的时刻”。 “我们正在尽力塞进去，”他补充道。 “我