tachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="梅兰妮·C 和蒂尔达·斯文顿。图片来源：Per Ole Hagen 和 Dave Benett via GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Melanie-C-and-Tilda-Swinton.-Credit-Per-Ole-Hagen-and-Dave-Benett-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Melanie-C-and-Tilda-Swinton.-Credit-Per-Ole-Hagen-and-Dave-Benett-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Melanie-C-and-Tilda-Swinton.-Credit-Per-Ole-Hagen-and-Dave-Benett-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Melanie-C-and-Tilda-Swinton.-Credit-Per-Ole-Hagen-and-Dave-Benett-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Melanie-C-and-Tilda-Swinton.-Credit-Per-Ole-Hagen-and-Dave-Benett-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Melanie-C-and-Tilda-Swinton.-Credit-Per-Ole-Hagen-and-Dave-Benett-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Orbital">Orbital</a>邀请<a href="/artists/melanie-c">Mel C</a>和<a href="/artists/Tilda-Swinton">蒂尔达·斯文顿 (Tilda Swinton)</a>作为特邀嘉宾出席今年<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">格拉斯顿伯里音乐</a>节的演出。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/orbital-we-were-banned-from-top-of-the-pops-for-being-utterly-boring-3555548">Orbital：“我们因为太无聊而被禁止参加 Top of the Pops！”</a></strong></li></ul><p>斯温顿在公园里打开了这对电子二人组的演出，他们穿着一件带有发光眼镜的白色长裙。 <em>“专注于一个地方，当那个地方吸引了你的全部注意力时，深呼吸/呼出并闭上眼睛，”</em>她在表演他们的歌曲“Deeper”时说，而 Orbital 从后面开始了当晚的第一首歌她。</p><p>当晚结束时，这位前运动辣妹加入了二人组的“Spicy”表演，这首歌曲采样了<a href="/artists/Spice-Girls">辣妹</a>组合唱片中的曲目，包括她们的热门歌曲“Wannabe”。这位歌手身穿发光眼镜和全白运动服，一边随着歌曲一边在公园舞台上跳跃、跳舞。</p><p>这标志着梅尔·C 连续第三次惊喜亮相沃西农场年度盛典。这对电子二人组最近在 BBC 节目中为 Jo Whiley 表演了这首歌。 “Spicy”是他们只现场演奏的一首曲目。 </p><figure id="attachment_3770307" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3770307" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3770307" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tilda-Swinton-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-BBC-Iplayer-screen-grab.jpg" alt="蒂尔达·斯文顿 (Tilda Swinton) 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 (Glastonbury) 上的表演。图片来源：BBC Iplayer 屏幕截图" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tilda-Swinton-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-BBC-Iplayer-screen-grab.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tilda-Swinton-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-BBC-Iplayer-screen-grab-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tilda-Swinton-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-BBC-Iplayer-screen-grab-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tilda-Swinton-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-BBC-Iplayer-screen-grab-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tilda-Swinton-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-BBC-Iplayer-screen-grab-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Tilda-Swinton-at-Glastonbury-2024.-Credit-BBC-Iplayer-screen-grab-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3770307" class="wp-caption-text">蒂尔达·斯文顿 (Tilda Swinton) 在 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 (Glastonbury) 上的表演。图片来源：BBC Iplayer 屏幕截图</figcaption></figure><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Orbital 现已在 Glastonbury 与 Tilda Swinton 一起现场演出——大规模的 FOMO。 1994 年，他们在格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 The Other Stage 上亮相。将舞曲音乐引入主流。 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Glastonbury2024?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Glastonbury2024</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Glastonbury24?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Glastonbury24</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Orbital?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Orbital</a> <a href="https://t.co/PQKutTHh58">pic.twitter.com/PQKutTHh58</a></p><p> - H (@Stanfield72) <a href="https://twitter.com/Stanfield72/status/1807147736992764006?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 6 月 29 日